data.description: Solar panels installed 2020!!! Electricity bill is $55/month! Roof 2017. A/C is a 2020 and has it's own electrical panel. Front and back screened porches. This house has a nice, natural flow. It's a split floor plan. The master has a huge bonus room attached to it which would be ideal for an office, nursery or even storage (there is a closet in this room as well). Indoor laundry room off the kitchen with more space for storage. The yard is fully fenced. There is room for RV or boat storage as well. You can even watch the rocket launches from your own front yard! This cute home is ready for it's new owners.
